Agol S: MOEA/D Tor MOMWB
Input: A MOMWB instance, trade-off set Λ, neighborhood size N ≥ 1
Output: S
∀λ  Λ, Bλ ← N nearest neighbors of λ in Λ (Euclidean distance);
∀λ  Λ, Pλ← a random sample from {0, 1}m,
S ← ;
while stopping conditions not met do
for λ  Λ do
x ← uniformly sampled from Pλ;
y ← independent bit flips on x with probability 1/m;
D ← {l  Bλ : ∀z  Pl, fi(y) < fi(z)};
T ← {l  B : ∀z  Pl, f(y) = fi(z)};
∀l  D, Pl ← {y};
∀l  T, Pl ← Pi U {y} removing solutions with duplicate images;
S ← non-dominated individuals in S U {y} under relation ≤a;
